         "try { } catch(e) {e;}; try { } catch(e$$1) {e$$1;}");
    test("try { } catch(e) {e; try { } catch(e) {e;}};",
         "try { } catch(e) {e; try { } catch(e$$1) {e$$1;} }; ");
